Lagos – Raphael Ademulegun, immediate past Chairman of Odigbo local government area of Ondo State has promised the people of Ondo South Senatorial district that he would give quality and effective representation if given the chance to represent them at the forthcoming 2019 general elections. He made the pledged on Thursday at the zonal meeting of the Ondo South of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) at the Catholic hall in Ode-Irele. Ademulegun who is a grassroot political mobilizer promised to deliver the senate seat for his party in the 2019 general election if given the ticket, stressing that he will not disappoint them if given the opportunity. He assured the mammoth crowd at the meeting that he would represent them with the fear of God being a committed Pastor in the vineyard of God. “I want to assure you my people of Ondo South Senatorial district that if given the opportunity to represent you, I will give quality and effective representation. “I also want to assure you all that, I as a grassroots moblizer as you all know promise to deliver the Senate seat for our great party in the 2019 general election if given the ticket and I will represent you with the fear of God,” he added. The meeting was attended by large number of enthusiastic party supporters. Also in attendance at the meeting are the big wigs of PDP in the Southern Senatorial District of Ondo State. Stakeholders present at the meeting also agreed that Ile-Oluji-Okeigbo/ Odigbo Federal Constituency of the state should produce the next senator for the zone. 0 comments Do you get a good or bad response from your wife after making love? Discover a great natural solution that changed my story and put an end to weak/premature ejaculation, CLICK HERE.  100% Natural Solution To Premature Ejaculation, Weak Erection, Watery Sperm, Other Sexual Dysfunctions And Last More Than 30 Minutes During Sex.